DeathSteel::

He grinned at the bot infront of him. He knew that this bot was 
easily insulted. So he would not arrouse anger in this bot just 
yet. "I am in need of a base and fellow predacons. I am new and wish 
to join a group that is an elite fighting force. I was assuming that 
this was the better of the other groups my ship scanned before it 
crashed. Perhaps, if you will not mind, I wish to join. I am 
currently seeking revenge against the maximals. They shot down my 
ship and left it to float in space for a while. I have been planning 
the death to the maximals for some time." he said, raw anger on his 
face plates.
